a212 6
   |                  |                              |
   |                  | The Z-packet-pc-mask         |
   |                  | attribute is used when       |
   |                  | passing Harvard-encoded PC   |
   |                  | addresses to the gdb         |
   |                  | component via a Z packet.    |
d294 29
a322 21
   +------------------------------------------------------+
   |                      attributes                      |
   |------------------------------------------------------|
   |      name      |category|  legal  |default|behaviors||
   |                |        | values  | value |         ||
   |----------------+--------+---------+-------+---------||
   |trace-gdbserv?  |-       |boolean  |false  |setting  ||
